{
  "schema_version": 1,
  "description": "Machine-readable verification manifest. Each target's command is an argv array executed with shell=False by .claude/scripts/phase5b_verify.py. The '## Source-of-Truth Commands' block in CLAUDE.md is the human-readable documentation of these same commands; this file is the executable source of truth.",
